      <title>特朗普关税计划可能颠覆贸易、引发食品通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-tariff-plan-risks-upending-trade-stoking-food-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普计划下个月对美国一些最大的农业贸易伙伴征收关税，这可能会颠覆市场并引发食品价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-tariff-plan-risks-upending-trade-stoking-food-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 23:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强或加剧新兴亚洲股市 540 亿美元资金外流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/strong-dollar-may-worsen-54-billion-exodus-from-em-asia-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的关税举措意味着美元复苏可能会成为亚洲股市的更大威胁，因为它会侵蚀经济增长放缓地区的降息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/strong-dollar-may-worsen-54-billion-exodus-from-em-asia-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推迟征收关税后亚洲股市将反弹：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普将美国对墨西哥和加拿大征收关税的期限推迟一个月，并表示将与中国进行进一步谈判，亚洲股市有望反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税扼杀了墨西哥的投资吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/trump-s-tariffs-killed-mexico-s-investment-appeal-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社观点专栏作家 JP Spinetto 解释道，无论该关税最终结果如何，墨西哥作为寻求进入美国市场的公司投资目的地的吸引力都已遭受不可挽回的损害。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/trump-s-tariffs-killed-mexico-s-investment-appeal-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:30:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zavolock：青睐电信、软件和国防部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/favor-telecoms-software-defense-sectors-zavolock-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席欧洲股票策略师 Marina Zavolock 看好欧洲电信、软件和国防类股，因为她对特朗普政府执政期间的股票走势进行了建模。她还看好美元盈利股，并表示航空航天业由于其定价能力更强，更能抵御关税。她在《开盘交易》节目中与彭博社的 Kriti Gupta、Guy Johnson 和 Anna Edwards 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/favor-telecoms-software-defense-sectors-zavolock-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:29:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韦格纳：关税将使欧洲经济增长前景恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/europe-growth-outlook-will-worsen-on-tariffs-wegner-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级的欧洲、中东和非洲主权评级主管 Malgorzata Wegner 表示，虽然“细节决定成败”，但如果征收关税，欧洲的增长前景将比预期更糟。她在《开盘交易》节目中与彭博社的 Guy Johnson 和 Anna Edwards 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/europe-growth-outlook-will-worsen-on-tariffs-wegner-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:28:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德博诺：对欧盟征收 10-15% 关税的基准情景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/baseline-scenario-of-10-15-tariffs-on-eu-debono-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pantheon Macroeconomics 高级欧洲经济学家 Melanie Debono 认为，欧盟的基本关税为 10-15%，对出口和投资的打击将很小。假设这种情况发生，她还认为欧洲央行将在 2025 年再降息两次。她在《彭博日报欧洲版》节目中接受了彭博社的 Tom Mackenzie 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/baseline-scenario-of-10-15-tariffs-on-eu-debono-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:21:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼协助推动移民政策，赫格塞斯访问南部边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/hegseth-visits-southern-border-as-pentagon-aids-immigration-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯前往美国与墨西哥的边境，这是他担任五角大楼负责人后的首次出访，他强调自己愿意让军方参与驱逐出境和移民执法工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/hegseth-visits-southern-border-as-pentagon-aids-immigration-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:52:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大股市收复八月以来最大盘中跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/canadian-stocks-could-see-major-correction-after-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普上周末表示，将从周二开始对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税，加拿大基准股指周一缩减跌幅，此前该指数一度创下自 8 月份以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/canadian-stocks-could-see-major-correction-after-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
